  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Zebaoṭ: Schinni Weetâ / kas mannâ Preekchaâ/ kas Dedsa-\npohstâ irr/ ka nedê Zilweks/nedê mo·Uppurus uppure/ nu Ehdâ-\nLohpt tur irr/ un wiſſôs winna mo·Uppurus eededsina/un Uppu-\nPileſahtôs buhs attat Gannu rus fataifa muhſchain.\nDshwokti / kas to gannamu\nPulku ſeek ganniteês."
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "13. Eekſch to Kalnu Pilſtah-\nteem/ un Eeleiju Pilſfahtôs/ un\neekſch teem Pilſfahteem prett\nDeenas-Widdus Puſſi / un\neekſch Benjamina Semmes/ un\napfahrt Jeruſalemes gullanahm\nWeetahm/ un eekſch teem Pilſ-\nfahteem Juha/ eeſt tee gannami\nPulki attat zauri appakſch to\nSkaititaju Rohkahm/ ſakka tas\nKUNGS.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "14. Rangt / tahê Deenas\nnahks/ ſakka tas KUNGS: Ka\nees to ſchebliu Wahrdü / ko es\nuhs Iſraëta Nammu/ un pahr\nto Nammu Juha efmu run-\nnajs/ padarrifchu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "15. Tannig Deenâs/ un tan-\nni Laikâ likſchu es Dahwidam\nweenu Sarru tahê Taitnibas\niſplaukt/ un tas darrihs Teeſu/\nun Taifnibu wits Semmes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "16. Tannig Deenâs taps\nJuha atpeſtita/ un Jeruſaleme\ndshwohs bes Bihjaſchanas/ un\nſchis irr tas (Wahrdê) ar ko\ntwinnu fanke: Tas KUNGS\nmuho Taifniba.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "17. Jo ta ſakka tas KUNGS:\nDahwidam ne peetrutks weens\nWihrs/ kas us to Goda-Krehf-\nlu ta Iſraëta Namma febsch.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "18. Ir teem Preestereem teem\nLeiviteem ue truhks weens Wihrs\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "19. Un ta KUNGA Wahrdê\nnotikke uhs Jeremiju/ un ſazzija:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "20. Ta ſakka tas KUNGS:\nJa juhs warrat iſnihzinaht man-\nnu Derribu tahê Deenas/ un\ntahê Nakts/ pehz ta/ ka Deena\nun Nakts ne irr ſawa Laikâ /\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "21. Tad ir taps iſnihzinata\nmannu Derriba ar mannu Kal-\npu Dahwidu/ ka tam ne buhtu\nne kahdê Dehle/ kas us winna\nGohda-Krehsin walda/ un ar\nteem Leuiteem manneem Sul-\nlaineem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "22. Itt ka tas Debbes\nSpehks ne warr ſkaitihts / un\ntahê Juhraê Smiltis ne warr\nmehrotas tapt/ tapatt wairoſchn\nes to Dſimmumu mannu Kalpa\nDahwida / un tahê Lewitus/\nkas man kalpo.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "23. Wehl notikke ta KUNGA\nWahrdê us Jeremiju/ un ſazzija:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "24. Ne effitu redſejs/ ko ſchee\nLaudis runna/ un ſakka? Tahê\nDiwi Ziltis/ ko tas KUNGS bij\niſtwehlejs/ irr winſch un atmet-\ntis/ un neewa mannu Laudis/\nitt ka tee wairs manni Laudis\nne buhtu preekſch winneem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "25. Ta ſakka tas KUNGS:\nJa es ſawu Derribu Deenas un\nNakts pehz (ne turru/) ja es\ntahê Debbes un tahê Semmes\nEkkumus ne efmu eezeblis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "26. Tad ir es atimettitchu\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
